text: Paulose I may refer to: *Baselios Paulose I (1836–1913), the first Catholicos of the East after its reinstatement in India. The First Catholicos of the Malankara Orthodox Syrian Church *Cyril Baselios I (1935-2007), Maphrian and the first Major Archbishop of the Syro-Malankara Catholic Church ==See also== *Paulose II (disambiguation)
title: Paulose I
